you can also use the 'while' Function too (though I've not done much testing with it, if there's any issues that come up):

```
// example scripting:

terminator_boolean_variable = false
while (not terminator_boolean_variable) {
  ask ("Stop?") {
    if (result) {
      terminator_boolean_variable = true
    }
  }
}
```
